title: P.O.S. - Episode 55
itunes:title: P.O.S. - Episode 55
description:
We spoke to the hip-hop artist and all around amazing dude, P.O.S. about growing up in the midwest, the intersection of punk & hip-hop as well as fatherhood and how that impacts his decisions. It was a very inspiring chat that I hope you enjoy. Brought to you in conjunction with Propertyofzack.com
